{"tid":1042200,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[海賊王 one piece] 今期OP單行本92 SBS 重要情報！！可能同卓洛有關！","createTime":"2019-03-01T11:39:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T13:38:19.000Z","uid":130563,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2971b41da9326f87abf2a4a292bc86d07770af5d","tid":1042200,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T11:39:10.000Z","msg":"讀者：909話的和之國裡出場的木匠老大，就是第7卷的SBS裡介紹的木匠「港友」吧？<br />\n<br />\n尾田：是的！！<br />\n當時有人問「風車村酒館門明明壞了 但回頭卻發現已經修好了 是誰幹的？！」時，介紹的「木匠港友」。<br />\n竟然在「新世界」的鎖國國家和之國裡！這當然奇怪吧？！<br />\n沒錯！其實這不是同一個人！姓氏是一樣，是因為雙方有血緣關係。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">其實幾十年前有和之國的船到達過「東海」。<br />\n而當時船上那些人中的一個後代就是大家都認識的某一個角色&hellip;<br />\n這個劇情可能會在正篇裡提及，所以就先不講了。<br />\n放心這不會是正篇故事，只是會稍微提一下。</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bbAmfRM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbbAmfRM.jpg&h=54e17a12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n==========<br />\n配合上一集卓洛識一個和之國古老方言，<br />\n卓洛個鄉下或者佢師傅都幾肯定同和之國有關啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CR9ih8D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCR9ih8D.png&h=243aa2a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3707ea81530821714a8854b3c0acf347b720333e","tid":1042200,"uid":197857,"like":14,"dislike":8,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T11:53:28.000Z","msg":"是撚旦啦<br />\n又係突然諗到突然加咋嘛<br />\n<br />\n不停咁加不停咁拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現哂形既垃圾"},{"pid":"079beb9ab0733d496ab1e8ac18e0cffefa794829","tid":1042200,"uid":3020,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:03:49.000Z","msg":"改到岩用為止<br />\n<br />\n生命卡今次都係得舊料"},{"pid":"a6bd1e554d591ab3277de4bc69f9aca3b6739214","tid":1042200,"uid":82404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:04:38.000Z","msg":"神伏筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces